        "total_confidence_boost": 0.25,
        "uniqueness_score": "HIGH",
        "notes": "CrewAI AMP uses Bearer token authentication. API endpoints return standard HTTP status codes (200, 400, 401, 404, 422, 500). Enterprise dashboard at app.crewai.com."
